Conclusions

Execution time of tested plots is generaly similar, there is no clear winner. Graphics requires more preprocessing of data, contour plots does not support facets. Lattice is more convenient thanks to formulas but plot customization is cumbersome. ggplot2 is the most convenient library with intuitive layer system and flexible customization.
